### Get my earnings as delivery boy
GET http://localhost:8000/api/earnings/my

### Get today's earnings as delivery boy
GET http://localhost:8000/api/earnings/today

### Get all earnings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/earnings

### Get earnings by delivery boy id
GET http://localhost:8000/api/earnings/delivery-boy/PASTE_DELIVERY_BOY_ID_HERE

### Mark earning as paid
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/earnings/PASTE_EARNING_ID_HERE/paid